that I clicked on the gray

00:12:07.770 --> 00:12:11.270
in the hopes that maybe a hidden
video model would disappear.

00:12:11.270 --> 00:12:14.150
I scrolled around the page
looking for player controls.

00:12:14.150 --> 00:12:16.640
I also hit the escape
key with no look.

00:12:16.640 --> 00:12:21.100
