00:26:57.360 --> 00:27:01.010
In April, 2021, FACIL'iti's
attorneys started sending letters

00:27:01.010 --> 00:27:02.840
demanding removal of any criticism.

00:27:03.880 --> 00:27:08.120
This letter to, probably going
to get the name wrong here,

00:27:08.120 --> 00:27:11.640
pronunciation wrong, this
letter to Koena shows two tweets

00:27:11.640 --> 00:27:12.640
about FACIL'iti.

