as to not only drop the sponsor,

00:28:30.260 --> 00:28:34.250
but to then issue a statement
rebuking its very existence.

00:28:34.250 --> 00:28:35.670
This part of the
statement stood out to me.

00:28:36.890 --> 00:28:39.150
"In particular,
it is the opinion of the board

00:28:39.150 --> 00:28:43.200
that AccessiBe peremptorily
and scornfully dismisses

00:28:43.200 --> 00:28:46.560
the concerns blind people have
